      <title>沙特阿拉伯房地产热潮将延续至 2025 年：世邦魏理仕（视频）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/saudi-arabia-real-estate-boom-to-extend-into-2025-cbre-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人口增长和外国人涌入推动了沙特阿拉伯房地产市场的飙升。世邦魏理仕沙特咨询业务主管 Elias Bou Habib 在彭博电视的“中东和非洲视野”节目中告诉 Joumanna Bercetche，该公司预计 2025 年房价和租金将上涨。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/saudi-arabia-real-estate-boom-to-extend-into-2025-cbre-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 06:24:26 GMT</pubDate>
